        "subject": "LU-3528 osp: commit on share for cross-MDT operation.",
        "message": "LU-3528 osp: commit on share for cross-MDT operation.\n\nAfter cross-MDT lock has been granted, it would check\nif the object version < last committed transno, if not,\ndo sync to make sure the current update of the object is\ncommitted to disk before further modification.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4719da6de7e47b645e21fedeae3d4259e99e62b3\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
